fore identical with <i>Elisheba</i>, the name of the wife of Aaron according to the genealogy at Exodus 6:23. The final element seems to have been altered by association with Hebrew <i>shabbāth</i> ‘Sabbath’."]}]}],"historicEvents":[{"id":1705197,"age":30,"year":"1455","julianDay":2252488,"title":"Wars of the Roses","description":"Wars of the Roses was a series of English civil wars for control of the throne of England between the royal families House of Lancaster and the House of York. The name of the war was derived as the red rose was the symbol of the Lancastrians and the white rose was the symbol of the Yorks.","url":"https://www.history.com/topics/british-history/wars-of-the-roses","urlTitle":"History - Wars of the Roses","jurisdictionLevel":2}],"lifeSummary":"Elizabeth Wildish was born in 1425, in Faversham, Kent, England. She married Edward Ackhurst in January 1887. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter. She died in 1500, in Sherborne, Dorset, England, United Kingdom, at the age of 75."},"et":{"1425–1500":"1425–1500","1450–1487":"1450–1487","1425":"1425","1500":"1500","1455":"1455","1487":"1487","about 1500":"umbes 1500","1450":"1450","about 1487":"umbes 1487","about 1450":"umbes 1450","Faversham, Kent, England":"Faversham, Kent, England","Holwell, Dorset, England, United Kingdom":"Holwell, Dorset, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Sherborne, Dorset, England, United Kingdom":"Sherborne, Dorset, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Dorset, England, United Kingdom":"Dorset, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1425–1500":"1425–1500","1450–1487":"1450–1487","1425":"1425","1500":"1500","1455":"1455","1487":"1487","about 1500":"noin 1500","1450":"1450","about 1487":"noin 1487","about 1450":"noin 1450","Faversham, Kent, England":"Faversham, Kent, England","Holwell, Dorset, England, United Kingdom":"Holwell, Dorset, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Sherborne, Dorset, England, United Kingdom":"Sherborne, Dorset, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Dorset, England, United